Class Core

java.lang.Object
java.util.concurrent.ForkJoinTask<Void>
java.util.concurrent.RecursiveAction
cz.cuni.mff.soukups3.VariantCaller.Core
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Runnable, Future<Void>
public class Core extends RecursiveAction implements Runnable
Core analyzes all Reads available from the provided ReadsProvider and reports the found variants to the provided VariantsManager. If ReadsProvider and VariantsManager are Thread-safe there can be more Cores running in parallel.
